568
00:41:26.424 --> 00:41:28.593
[Pops sighs] We hid in the woods.

569
00:41:28.844 --> 00:41:31.555
It's personal for Kostya and me
with them krauts.


570
00:41:31.888 --> 00:41:33.557
And now because of my friend.

571
