706
00:47:25.617 --> 00:47:28.119
I've done nothing wrong. I beg of you!

707
00:47:28.286 --> 00:47:29.370
[Vera sobs]

708
00:47:29.537 --> 00:47:31.748
[Klein] Commander, I knew it.

709
00:47:33.833 --> 00:47:35.376
