We have a truck!

829
01:00:12.383 --> 01:00:13.342
Koch?

830
01:00:13.509 --> 01:00:14.468
Yes?

831
01:00:14.635 --> 01:00:17.263
Shoot at the Banya and distract him.
You understand?


832
01:00:17.763 --> 01:00:18.722
Yes, sir.

833
01:00:19.056 --> 01:00:20.182
Koch's hurt!

834
01:00:21.016 --> 01:00:21.976
I'm fine.

835
01:00:22.268 --> 01:00:23.269
Just a scratch.

836
01:00:24.561 --> 01:00:26.188
[suspenseful music]

837
01:00:39.785 --> 01:00:40.744
After three.

838
01:00:41.328 --> 01:00:42.288
Okay.

839
01:00:43.122 --> 01:00:44.081
One...

840
01:00:47.209 --> 01:00:48.168
Two...

841
01:00:51.297 --> 01:00:52.256
Three!

842
01:00:53.632 --> 01:00:54.717
[Wulf gasps]

843
01:01:02.016 --> 01:01:03.142
[Wulf grunts]

844
01:01:17.698 --> 01:01:19.742
[suspenseful music intensifies]

845
01:01:32.087 --> 01:01:33.464
You, there!

846
01:01:33.630 --> 01:01:34.715
Don't give me orders!

847
01:02:32.231 --> 01:02:35.025
[Pops] Oh my God, 
I can't move so fast.

848
01:02:47.329 --> 01:02:48.580
What do you see?

849
01:02:50.249 --> 01:02:51.208
He's gone.

850
01:03:06.473 --> 01:03:07.433
Kostya,

851
01:03:08.058 --> 01:03:09.017
the door.

852
01:03:19.611 --> 01:03:21.363
[Red Ghost gasping]

853
01:03:39.339 --> 01:03:40.299
My God,

854
01:03:41.383 --> 01:03:42.759
it's really him?

855
01:03:43.469 --> 01:03:45.095
-Who?
-The Ghost.


856
01:03:45.345 --> 01:03:46.305
Who do you think?

857
01:03:48.807 --> 01:03:50.058
Check how he is!

858
01:03:54.062 --> 01:03:55.355
-Breathing.
-Good.


859
01:03:55.689 --> 01:03:56.732
He doesn't...

860
01:03:57.065 --> 01:03:58.525
die so easily.

861
01:03:58.984 --> 01:04:01.195
Did you see how many Germans he killed?

862
01:04:02.070 --> 01:04:03.030
This man's...

863
01:04:03.864 --> 01:04:04.948
a proud warrior.

864
01:04:11.497 --> 01:04:12.956
It's for Kostya, this bread.

865
01:04:13.165 --> 01:04:15.375
Uh-huh. Go take it over to him.

866
01:04:18.128 --> 01:04:19.087
Commander,

867
01:04:19.546 --> 01:04:22.174
did you see
how I killed the machine gunner?


868
01:04:22.549 --> 01:04:23.967
My eyes, they're still sharp.

869
01:04:24.218 --> 01:04:26.136
And the Germans, they shat their pants!

870
01:04:27.054 --> 01:04:28.972
[Pops and Vera laughs]

871
01:04:29.264 --> 01:04:32.643
I knew something bad would happen
when you guys decided to leave.


872
01:04:32.809 --> 01:04:33.769
Me, too.

873
01:04:34.436 --> 01:04:35.395
[Vera laughs]

874
01:04:43.529 --> 01:04:45.405
Here you go, Kostya. Eat.

875
01:04:48.408 --> 01:04:49.368
Water!

876
01:04:59.962 --> 01:05:00.921
You bastard!

877
01:05:01.296 --> 01:05:02.714
Everyone's against me.

878
01:05:06.051 --> 01:05:07.094
[Klein sighs]

879
01:05:07.553 --> 01:05:09.304
I'm telling you, we're right here.

880
01:05:09.638 --> 01:05:11.098
And where is Taraskovo?

881
01:05:11.265 --> 01:05:13.308
-This here is Taraskovo.
-And the Germans?


882
01:05:13.475 --> 01:05:14.434
Just here.

883
01:05:14.977 --> 01:05:17.396
Then we go via Taraskovo.

884
01:05:17.563 --> 01:05:18.564
I know it well.

885
01:05:18.814 --> 01:05:20.566
I know every stone, 
I know it well.

886
01:05:20.774 --> 01:05:22.192
That's with maps or no maps.

887
01:05:22.401 --> 01:05:23.735
I know every pine tree.

888
01:05:23.902 --> 01:05:26.780
<i>-I don't need a map.
-Where'd your friend hide his booze?</i>


889
01:05:26.989 --> 01:05:28.824
Is that all you think of?

890
01:05:28.991 --> 01:05:31.868
I can't believe you'd ask about booze
at a time like this.


891
01:05:34.037 --> 01:05:36.164
There's so much food! Hot food,

892
01:05:36.331 --> 01:05:37.332
even a sauna.

893
01:05:37.583 --> 01:05:40.377
I guarantee you
there's booze here somewhere!


894
01:05:40.586 --> 01:05:41.545
I'm covered in lice!

895
01:05:41.837 --> 01:05:44.506
[Commissary] Sergeant, look at this.
A hole, here,


896
01:05:44.673 --> 01:05:45.757
in the German' front.

897
01:05:46.091 --> 01:05:47.175
With a little luck,

898
01:05:47.342 --> 01:05:48.969
we will find our people tomorrow.

899
01:05:49.344 --> 01:05:50.846
What do we do with that guy?

900
01:05:51.013 --> 01:05:52.723
We carry him around like a king?

901
01:05:52.889 --> 01:05:54.558
If necessary, we will.

902
01:05:54.766 --> 01:05:55.767
Now that's enough!

903
01:05:56.018 --> 01:05:57.603
Just get ready to go, will you?

904
01:05:58.145 --> 01:05:59.730
[Vera screams]

905
01:06:03.817 --> 01:06:04.943
Oh, it's coming.

906
01:06:06.153 --> 01:06:07.112
It's coming!

907
01:06:14.828 --> 01:06:16.204
What the hell are you doing?

908
01:06:16.413 --> 01:06:17.581
What are you doing?

909
01:06:18.081 --> 01:06:19.041
Arman?

910
01:06:19.791 --> 01:06:21.418
Two more over here! This minute!

911
01:06:22.044 --> 01:06:25.422
Listen to me, Arman.
We're losing precious time.


912
01:06:26.131 --> 01:06:28.091
It's taking way too long.

913
01:06:29.217 --> 01:06:30.177
What?

914
01:06:40.520 --> 01:06:42.356
Who the hell is that?

915
01:06:43.148 --> 01:06:45.025
[Braun panting]

916
01:07:16.181 --> 01:07:17.349
Wonderful.

917
01:07:24.189 --> 01:07:26.483
[Sailor] Kostya, open the door for me.

918
01:07:28.694 --> 01:07:30.779
I can't believe our group is growing.

919
01:07:31.571 --> 01:07:32.572
A new member!

920
01:07:33.365 --> 01:07:34.616
What a surprise!

921
01:07:42.541 --> 01:07:44.251
-[Vera screaming]
-[Pops] Come on!


922
01:07:44.501 --> 01:07:46.294
I just need to grab your legs!

923
01:07:46.878 --> 01:07:48.338
Push! Push! Push! Push!

924
01:07:48.547 --> 01:07:49.923
That's right. Yep. Yep.

925
01:07:50.090 --> 01:07:51.049
Right, right!

926
01:07:51.216 --> 01:07:53.343
With God's help,
you can do this. Come on,


927
01:07:53.510 --> 01:07:55.721
you just need to breathe.
Breathe, breathe.


928
01:07:55.971 --> 01:07:57.097
Like this.

929
01:07:57.431 --> 01:07:58.390
Like that.

930
01:07:58.598 --> 01:07:59.850
What are they doing here?

931
01:08:00.475 --> 01:08:01.977
Out with you! Go on! Get out!

932
01:08:02.144 --> 01:08:03.145
-Right now!
-Stay!


933
01:08:03.311 --> 01:08:04.312
Is this your first?

934
01:08:05.105 --> 01:08:06.815
I've delivered three babies before.

935
01:08:07.107 --> 01:08:08.608
Here comes number four.

936
01:08:08.984 --> 01:08:11.987
Hold her tight! Push! Push!
Push! That's it, good.


937
01:08:13.029 --> 01:08:15.323
-[Vera screams]
-[Pops] Come on, girl! Yeah!


938
01:08:15.615 --> 01:08:17.576
That's it! Come on, girl.
You can do it.


939
01:08:17.743 --> 01:08:19.828
With God's help,
you'll soon give birth.


940
01:08:20.162 --> 01:08:21.705
<i>-No, I can't!
-You can!</i>


941
01:08:21.872 --> 01:08:24.040
Of course you can! 
Back in the past,

942
01:08:24.249 --> 01:08:26.001
women gave birth in haystacks.

943
01:08:26.209 --> 01:08:28.295
-They didn't make a fuss about it!
-No!


944
01:08:28.462 --> 01:08:31.089
-Hold her! You're almost there!
-I don't want to!


945
01:08:31.715 --> 01:08:33.133
Why so quiet?

946
01:08:33.800 --> 01:08:35.469
You have an anecdote or something?

947
01:08:36.052 --> 01:08:37.012
About what?

948
01:08:37.888 --> 01:08:40.348
-The one about sparrows.
-Oh.


949
01:08:42.809 --> 01:08:45.103
So, a Russian asks
for a bottle of vodka.

950
01:08:45.645 --> 01:08:47.773
He drank a bottle, and then got another.

951
01:08:48.106 --> 01:08:49.441
And then he drank that one.

952
01:08:49.691 --> 01:08:52.569
And then he gets a third bottle.
And by now he's getting...


953
01:08:52.903 --> 01:08:54.654
just really, really drunk.

954
01:08:55.447 --> 01:08:57.073
-I can't!
-Come on, come on!


955
01:08:57.240 --> 01:08:58.784
Now, breathe like that. Go on!

956
01:08:58.950 --> 01:08:59.910
Go on!

957
01:09:00.410 --> 01:09:02.120
Do it like I showed you. That's it.

958
01:09:02.287 --> 01:09:03.789
Well, he takes the gun, and...

959
01:09:04.080 --> 01:09:06.249
shoots the sparrow
into a thousand pieces.


960
01:09:07.042 --> 01:09:08.919
The Germans ask, "How are you able...

961
01:09:09.127 --> 01:09:10.086
to hit it?"

962
01:09:10.462 --> 01:09:11.713
And the Russian replied:

963
01:09:12.130 --> 01:09:15.675
"It's really not a problem
when you've had four bottles,


964
01:09:16.092 --> 01:09:17.803
then there are sparrows everywhere!

965
01:09:18.720 --> 01:09:20.096
[Vera grunting]

966
01:09:20.472 --> 01:09:21.765
[Pops] Yes! Push!

967
01:09:22.182 --> 01:09:23.183
That's funny.

968
01:09:23.433 --> 01:09:24.935
Tell me it's going to be okay!

969
01:09:25.143 --> 01:09:28.021
-Please tell me it'll be okay!
-Just imagine it's all over.


970
01:09:28.188 --> 01:09:29.481
It will be over very soon.

971
01:09:29.648 --> 01:09:32.150
It's like,
it's like when you need to take a shit.


972
01:09:32.609 --> 01:09:34.528
-But you can'!
-Breathe! And breathe.


973
01:09:34.694 --> 01:09:36.947
That's it! That's it!
That's it! That's it!


974
01:09:37.989 --> 01:09:38.949
Here.

975
01:09:39.199 --> 01:09:40.826
-[Vera screaming]
-[Pops] Push!


976
01:09:41.117 --> 01:09:42.077
What is it?

977
01:09:42.494 --> 01:09:43.787
The Ghost had it on him.

978
01:09:44.079 --> 01:09:45.580
It's him as a child. I think.

979
01:09:46.540 --> 01:09:48.416
He looked very different as a child.

980
01:09:49.417 --> 01:09:50.418
As did I.

981
01:09:50.794 --> 01:09:52.379
-Return it.
-I'll give it back.


982
01:09:52.546 --> 01:09:54.130
-Push! And push!
-[Vera screams]


983
01:09:54.297 --> 01:09:55.257
Yeah, well done!

984
01:09:55.549 --> 01:09:57.717
[Pops laughs] Well, look at that!

985
01:09:57.968 --> 01:09:58.927
Hold on.

986
01:10:00.136 --> 01:10:01.930
There he is. There he is.

987
01:10:04.057 --> 01:10:05.141
It's all done.

988
01:10:05.392 --> 01:10:06.726
-That's it now.
-My baby.


989
01:10:06.893 --> 01:10:08.353
That's it. It's done.

990
01:10:08.728 --> 01:10:09.729
[Pops laughs]

991
01:10:10.146 --> 01:10:11.106
Yeah.

992
01:10:11.273 --> 01:10:12.232
Blabber-mouth!

993
01:10:13.149 --> 01:10:14.776
Come here now! Come here!

994
01:10:15.110 --> 01:10:16.611
Now, get me a knife.

995
01:10:19.030 --> 01:10:21.157
No, hold it over the fire.

996
01:10:24.035 --> 01:10:24.995
My child.

997
01:10:25.203 --> 01:10:26.162
Yes.

998
01:10:26.913 --> 01:10:29.457
God guide my hand.
God be with me.


999
01:10:29.833 --> 01:10:30.792
Right then.

1000
01:10:31.334 --> 01:10:32.294
All done!

1001
01:10:32.794 --> 01:10:33.753
That's it.

1002
01:10:34.588 --> 01:10:36.965
-It's a boy? If's a boy?
-Finished. Yes.


1003
01:10:37.173 --> 01:10:38.550
-It's a boy?
-Yes. Yes it is.


1004
01:10:39.217 --> 01:10:40.510
[Pops laughs]

1005
01:10:40.844 --> 01:10:41.803
And you said...

1006
01:10:42.345 --> 01:10:43.471
you couldn't do it.

1007
01:10:43.847 --> 01:10:44.931
Well, you did.

1008
01:10:45.140 --> 01:10:46.558
[Pops laughs]

1009
01:10:46.766 --> 01:10:48.101
"I don't want to."

1010
01:10:48.518 --> 01:10:50.520
[Pops laughs]

1011
01:10:52.022 --> 01:10:53.523
[dramatic music]

1012
01:11:11.291 --> 01:11:13.793
The Germans must be coming.
He can smell them.


1013
01:11:32.729 --> 01:11:35.023
[Pops] Yes, I know.
I know, I know, I know!


1014
01:11:37.442 --> 01:11:39.152
Get ready for battle.

1015
01:11:40.612 --> 01:11:42.864
[dramatic music intensifies]

1016
01:12:03.093 --> 01:12:05.095
-There's only five.
-How many?


1017
01:12:06.221 --> 01:12:08.640
You must be joking, Commander.

1018
01:12:09.224 --> 01:12:11.351
I didn't hear what you said.

1019
01:12:11.518 --> 01:12:13.061
How many enemies you have said?

1020
01:12:13.561 --> 01:12:16.690
Five? And how many soldiers did you have
under your command?


1021
01:12:17.065 --> 01:12:18.858
Arman! Arman!

1022
01:12:19.693 --> 01:12:21.194
Haul out.

1023
01:12:21.444 --> 01:12:22.404
Yes, sir.

1024
01:12:22.612 --> 01:12:23.738
Oh, wait...

1025
01:12:25.407 --> 01:12:28.785
or maybe you were attacked by
five Red Ghosts?


1026
01:12:32.956 --> 01:12:34.582
[suspenseful music]

1027
01:12:44.300 --> 01:12:45.552
There is no ghost.

1028
01:12:45.927 --> 01:12:48.013
Just a handful of half-frozen Partisans.

1029
01:12:49.556 --> 01:12:51.933
Grenade launcher! Fire!

1030
01:13:00.692 --> 01:13:02.485
Get away from here! Come on!

1031
01:13:02.652 --> 01:13:03.611
Fire!

1032
01:13:17.959 --> 01:13:20.045
[Vera crying]

1033
01:13:27.886 --> 01:13:30.430
Get away and hide! Wait! Wait!

1034
01:13:31.056 --> 01:13:33.141
-[somber music]
-Forgive me, son.


1035
01:13:33.892 --> 01:13:35.060
For everything.

1036
01:13:35.226 --> 01:13:36.394
Please forgive me.

1037
01:13:40.440 --> 01:13:41.441
Go on! Go on!

1038
01:13:41.608 --> 01:13:42.567
Go on!

1039
01:13:44.944 --> 01:13:46.446
[suspenseful music]

1040
01:13:47.155 --> 01:13:48.114
Fire!

1041
01:14:02.253 --> 01:14:03.880
I dare you to come closer.

1042
01:14:05.215 --> 01:14:06.674
[Sailor] Take your positions!

1043
01:14:06.883 --> 01:14:08.051
The Germans, there!

1044
01:14:09.803 --> 01:14:10.887
[Vera screams]

1045
01:14:26.027 --> 01:14:28.530
Now, just a little closer.

1046
01:14:29.155 --> 01:14:30.615
Closer.

1047
01:14:31.116 --> 01:14:32.492
A bit more.

1048
01:14:33.701 --> 01:14:34.661
German pig!

1049
01:14:34.869 --> 01:14:36.287
See if you can take me alive!

1050
01:14:49.634 --> 01:14:52.262
-[baby cries]
-It's okay. It's okay, my love.


1051
01:14:52.595 --> 01:14:54.180
Give me a couple of soldiers,

1052
01:14:54.514 --> 01:14:56.141
and I'll take care of it myself.

1053
01:14:57.267 --> 01:14:58.226
Colonel,

1054
01:14:59.310 --> 01:15:00.562
give me the chance...

1055
01:15:00.979 --> 01:15:02.397
to restore my honor.

1056
01:15:05.775 --> 01:15:07.152
Very well.

1057
01:15:07.652 --> 01:15:09.529
[suspenseful music continues]

1058
01:15:10.655 --> 01:15:11.823
Forward!

1059
01:15:13.741 --> 01:15:14.701
[Braun] Go!

1060
01:15:19.622 --> 01:15:20.582
Faster.

1061
01:15:23.459 --> 01:15:25.170
Go on, taste my lead then!

1062
01:15:26.087 --> 01:15:27.505
[baby crying]

1063
01:15:29.382 --> 01:15:30.508
How many are there?

1064
01:15:30.675 --> 01:15:31.634
Three.

1065
01:15:32.177 --> 01:15:33.261
Try this for size!

1066
01:15:37.348 --> 01:15:38.975
[baby crying]

1067
01:15:41.019 --> 01:15:41.978
Throw me the gun!

1068
01:15:46.482 --> 01:15:48.109
Come and get it, suckers!

1069
01:15:51.529 --> 01:15:52.488
Fire.

1070
01:15:53.406 --> 01:15:55.575
[dramatic music]

1071
01:16:00.205 --> 01:16:01.164
Fire.

1072
01:16:10.465 --> 01:16:11.424
Fire.

1073
01:16:15.970 --> 01:16:16.930
Louder!

1074
01:16:28.608 --> 01:16:32.111
At my command, you, you,
and you, with me.


1075
01:16:34.697 --> 01:16:35.657
Right...

1076
01:16:36.115 --> 01:16:37.075
now.

1077
01:16:37.283 --> 01:16:38.576
Now you can answer to God.

1078
01:16:39.285 --> 01:16:41.246
Ok, you and you. Charge!

1079
01:16:55.593 --> 01:16:58.513
[Commissary screaming]

1080
01:17:18.449 --> 01:17:19.951
Shitting yourself, huh?

1081
01:17:24.539 --> 01:17:25.832
Damn pigs!

1082
01:17:26.374 --> 01:17:27.333
Forward!

1083
01:17:28.918 --> 01:17:30.086
Faster! Faster!

1084
01:17:32.380 --> 01:17:33.881
[soldiers shouting]

1085
01:17:49.272 --> 01:17:50.481
You son of a bitch!

1086
01:18:02.035 --> 01:18:04.495
-Calm down, darling. Calm down.
-[baby crying]


1087
01:18:06.539 --> 01:18:07.790
It's okay! It's okay!

1088
01:18:09.208 --> 01:18:10.460
Now you're gonna get it!

1089
01:18:15.048 --> 01:18:16.174
Give me that gun!

1090
01:18:16.549 --> 01:18:17.717
Faster!

1091
01:18:18.926 --> 01:18:20.053
The munition.

1092
01:18:32.523 --> 01:18:34.359
What are you doing? 
Give me the gun!

1093
01:18:35.777 --> 01:18:38.029
-[baby sobbing]
-Oh, baby.


1094
01:18:44.285 --> 01:18:45.411
[baby sobbing]

1095
01:18:51.376 --> 01:18:52.460
It's all fine.

1096
01:18:55.338 --> 01:18:56.631
Well that shut them up.

1097
